Nightlight:

"Trinity enjoyed when she played with you, you fell unconscious,  she 
got worried... enough to search help for you she looks you like big-
brother, like a friend ... it isn't enough? Aeotaur didn't like 
reprogram you; plus Perplex liked that you stay with us, and he 
personally lead you to cr's... When you was worried about your 
flashbacks, Windlord promised help you to find out what's 
happening..." Said Nightlight "In this battle, Grouded risk his life 
to save you when you fell wounded, without that help you could have 
died...  All those things can you forget them?"
